sequenceDiagram
    participant Clock as Sim Clock
    participant Dir as Shift Director
    participant WO as Work Order Queue
    participant Agent as Specialist Agent
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant SSE as SSE Stream
    participant UI as Ops Console

    Clock->>Dir: Phase transition (morning_intake)
    Dir->>WO: Generate 21 work orders
    Dir->>SSE: phase_start:morning_intake
    SSE-->>UI: Live event update

    loop Agent Tick Cycle (~2.4s)
        Agent->>WO: Claim next work order (by priority)
        WO-->>Agent: WorkOrder (ASSIGNED)
        Agent->>SSE: started:{wo_type}
        SSE-->>UI: Action in lane
        Agent->>DB: Execute task (resolve ticket / sweep SLA / create patch)
        Agent->>DB: Log audit event
        Agent->>WO: Complete work order
        Agent->>SSE: completed:{wo_type} + KPIs
        SSE-->>UI: KPI cards update + feed entry
    end

    Note over Dir,UI: Phase advances at 35% → midday_it_ops, 70% → endofday_audit

    Agent->>DB: Generate PDF artifact
    Agent->>SSE: completed:monthly_ops_package + artifact
    SSE-->>UI: Artifact appears in panel
